{
  "stem": "17001.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 162.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, he came quite often to select us because being that we stayed in Auschwitz from-- like almost the middle or from end of May until end of November, which very few people who stayed that length of a time in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So unfortunately, we had encountered his selections many, many times.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were times that he was selecting for the skinny ones.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I would try to perfect my sister.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I would always look at a skinny girl when she was going.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's when I would put my sister after her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I figure that Mengele would select her so then my sister would slide through, and it-- many times it worked.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By that time, we were so experienced.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We know that when he's selecting the skinny ones, that goes to the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When he's-- there was this old man whom they claim that that's Mengele's father.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He came and he spoke perfect Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that's-- I-- I don't know if he was or not.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But among us, it was that that's Grandpa Mengele.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he said perfect Hungarian, my dear children, I'm a doctor.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And whoever has any problem, any pain, any sickness, you just come over to me and we will cure you and we will make you well enough, and you should have faith in us.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Meantime, the Blockalteste had warned us that these things will happen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And if you have a toothache or if you have a stomachache, it doesn't mean you're ready for the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So do not volunteer that you will be taken to a beautiful hospital and you will be given food, because you will not.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
